title: Bajrang Dal activist murder 2 BJP leaders receive threats on Facebook
text:
Bajrang Dal activist murder: 2 BJP leaders receive threats on Facebook 
India Today Sunday 25th October, 2015 
Five days after the police nabbed eight people in connection with the 
killing of a Bajrang Dal activist for allegedly expressing opposition to 
cattle trafficking, two BJP leaders on Saturday claimed that they 
received threats on their Facebook accounts....
